title.narrative: Advocacy, Partnerships and Communication: The rights of children in Myanmar are better promoted through effective advocacy, partnerships and communication.

description.narrative: UNICEF Myanmar continued to build its advocacy partnerships with Parliamentarians, youth, religious leaders and the media to help build an environment conducive to the realisation of children's rights especially for hard to reach children. UNICEF engaged these partners to take action on UNICEF's key advocacy priorities - Responding to COVID-19 in Myanmar, the 2020 Election, children in Rakhine, and children affected by armed conflict. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:05/08/2020
